title: Chelsea continuing to prove doubters wrong to the delight of James
description: Chelsea captain Reece James revelled in proving the Blues’ Champions League doubters wrong after their huge 1-0 win over Manchester United on Friday. James played a crucial role in the only goal of the game, neatly turning before providing the cross for Marc Cucurella to head home the winner in the 71st minute. title: Amorim pleased with ´competitive´ Man Utd ahead of Europa League final
